        [
          "1. You were ghouled after the war"
        ],
        [
          "2. You have served Pieterzoon as a ghoul since 1963"
        ],
        [
          "3. You do not have any interest in politics beyond making sure the clan is successful and you get to do your job."
        ],
        [
          "4. You believe in loyalty, the only reason you are looking for a new \"boss\" is your boss has been in torpor for about two years and is expected to remain there for a looong time"
        ],
        [
          "5. You like to fight, you came to LA to do that"
        ],
        [
          "6. You think that working for a man who understand the military but is not actually very good at it means you can do everything you want fight wise"
        ],
        [
          "7. You do not look for trouble, you solve it"
